{"tid":2379242,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"馬雲贈年輕人的三句話 - 馮睎乾","createTime":"2021-01-25T05:57:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-25T06:05:48.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"17d44f7a6254a237dff9c42ffc4f7133851fb48f","tid":2379242,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T05:57:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20210125/CVS6ST4RYRB5TKP5IAZYZSVAXU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20210125%2FCVS6ST4RYRB5TKP5IAZYZSVAXU%2F&d=Bi029C%2FGDe0wU7DInIQABQUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=6a723414\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20210125%2FCVS6ST4RYRB5TKP5IAZYZSVAXU%2F&h=710911e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20210125/CVS6ST4RYRB5TKP5IAZYZSVAXU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n馬雲贈年輕人的三句話 - 馮睎乾<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/K-z_-GPHQprjAIPSGLtiHoHwfYg=/960x960/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YD7TQDFZHVD2PHUSVY4X6WXIUE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FK-z_-GPHQprjAIPSGLtiHoHwfYg%3D%2F960x960%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYD7TQDFZHVD2PHUSVY4X6WXIUE.png&h=39e4c809&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n網民戲言，如果2021年馬雲要送給年輕人三句話，可能是：「你們是誰？」「你們要幹嘛？」「你們要帶我去哪裏？」這三句話，儘管馬雲並未說過，卻以自己的生命演繹出來，論教育意味，比他過往金句加起來都更深刻。<br />\n<br />\n據聞朱元璋老婆說過，富可敵國者是。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n岔開一筆，此事雖見《明史》，。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。不過他本月20號能夠露面報平安，透過視訊為「鄉村教師獎頒獎典禮」致詞，也許表示他已痛悟前非，甚至接了另一角色&mdash;&mdash;像那所謂美女網紅李子柒一樣，成為「中國農村青年致富帶頭人推廣大使」。<br />\n<br />\n很多媒體報道，只強調馬雲專注「教育公益」，錯了重點。馬雲說得很清楚，「我們這一代企業經營者的責任和擔當」是發展鄉村，又說「未來鄉村生活一定會越來越美好」，「越來越多的年輕人會回到鄉村」。還看不出是「上山下鄉2.0」？馬雲對年輕人真正要說的是：「你們是知青。」「你們要接受貧下中農的再教育。」「你們要到鄉村裏去。」"},{"pid":"8ebdd18218a2a7d5c34c0b0c3697acc2bd9e9162","tid":2379242,"uid":235015,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-25T06:05:48.000Z","msg":"某日<br />\n<br />\n公安：（拍門聲）...開門！<br />\n<br />\n馬雲出去開門<br />\n<br />\n3秒後<br />\n<br />\n馬雲：你們是誰？！你們要幹嘛？！你們要帶我去哪裏？！"}]}